title: Various Artists - No New York [1978/Ogg/q8]
description:
Legendary compilation of No Wave bands produced by Brian Eno. Features James Chance and the Contortions, Teenage Jesus and the Jerks (Lydia Lunch&#039;s first band), Mars, and D.N.A. (Arto Lindsay&#039;s first band).

Originally released in 1978.
